    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury performance and everyday reliability. Finished in a deep metallic charcoal that catches the light beautifully, the exterior remains in impressive shape with only minor, age-appropriate stone chips on the front fascia that do not detract from its overall curb appeal. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine, smoke-free cabin featuring supple leather upholstery that has been regularly conditioned; while there is light entry wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster, the passenger and rear seats look nearly untouched. Every feature, from the responsive infotainment screen to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car has been treated with the utmost care, boasting a documented service history that includes a recent synthetic oil change and a fresh set of high-performance all-season tires with over 80% tread remaining. It shifts smoothly through all gears, brakes with confidence, and offers a quiet, composed ride free of any unusual rattles or vibrations. This is a turn-key opportunity for a buyer who values a well-maintained machine that looks as good as it drives.",
